    %h3 Privacy Policy
    %p The following policy dictates the manner in which Listwerk collects and uses information gathered from users of this service.

    %h4 Privacy
    %p Your privacy is extremely important to us and we are committed to safeguarding the information you entrust to us. Listwerk will not disclose information about customers or users without express permission unless the release of said information is required by government subpoena.

    %h4 Information Collection
    %p Listwerk may collect personally identifiable information from Users in a variety of ways, including through online forms and other instances where Users are invited to volunteer such information. We may also collect information about how Users interact with our website . This information is obtained through analysis of server logs and through the use of "cookies" placed on user machines. A cookie is a piece of software that a Web server can store on a PC to identify the User should they visit the website again. While not all of the information that we collect from Users is personally identifiable, it may be associated with personally identifiable information that Users provide us through our website.

    %h4 Information Usage
    %p Listwerk may use personally identifiable information collected through our website to contact Users regarding the service. We may also use anonymized information collected through our website in order to identify future improvements to the service.

    %h4 Information Disclosure
    %p Listwerk will not disclose information about customers or users without express permission unless the release of said information is required by a trusted affiliate to facilitate action requested by the client, or is required by government subpoena. However, we may transfer information collected from Users in connection with a sale of our business.

    %h4 User Lists
    %p Your lists are viewable only by logging into your account (or if they are shared with other users). It is your responsibility to keep your password private.

    %h4 Questions
    %p Please contact us with any questions regarding our privacy policy by email support@Listwerk.com.

    %h3 Terms of Use

    %h4 Accounts
    %p The free version of Listwerk allows for the creation of up to three lists. A full version of Listwerk allows for unlimited lists and costs $25 USD per year. You will be automatically billed each year and may cancel or downgrade to the free version at any time. If you do not make a payment by its due date, your account will be downgraded to the free version after 10 days. You are responsible for any use of your account; consequently, you are responsible for keeping your account password and the keys you use to access the service secure.
      
    %h4 Cancellation and Refunds
    %p You may cancel your account at any time by accessing you account page and clicking the "Cancel my Account" link.  Your account data and personal information will be deleted upon cancelling your account. 

    %h4 Referrals
    %p Each time you invite (using your unique invite URL) or share a list with someone who subsequently purchases the full version of Listwerk, you will receive a free month of the full version of Listwerk. There is no limit to the number of free months you can receive.


